item arrival instead of sleeping a fixed min_batch_interval, removing the ~1s
trace-visibility latency floor. The prompt described the exact fix (blocking
get on first item + non-blocking drain), a list of hard invariants to
preserve, and required a latency regression test + a prompt-shutdown test.
Commit locally only; do NOT push / open a PR.

